prompts.prompt: A vibrant collage featuring a smiling woman in a flowing red dress with a pink-red dupatta. Surrounded by watercolor strawberries, cherries, envelopes, and a vintage vinyl record, the image radiates whimsy and romance with an aged paper background.

An ultra-realistic black and white studio portrait (9:16) of a confident person in an oversized black blazer and long skirt, seated casually on a chair. The minimalist white background features graffiti doodles in black, white, and orange with words like 'PURPOSE' and 'CREATE YOUR PATH'.

A young woman with long dark hair smiles while adjusting her blue and gold saree. She wears a necklace and stands against a textured wall with a floral border and a silver butterfly graphic. Text overlay reads 'YOU ARE MY CHARM IN THE CHAOS'.
A young woman takes a selfie, wearing a striped tan and white top with tan trousers. Her background features minimalist vertical stripes and beige heart motifs, exuding a modern Pinterest aesthetic.

A cheerful woman with long dark hair wearing a white saree with blue teardrop patterns smiles gently. She’s outlined like a sticker against a two-toned brown background with dashed hearts and wavy textures, giving a warm, hand-crafted aesthetic.

A young woman in traditional Indian attire holds her phone, hiding her face. The collage features handwritten notes, dried flowers, and cutouts with phrases like 'TRUST' and 'Love yourself'. The deep red and earthy tones evoke a soulful vintage look.

A young woman with dark braided hair in a floral top rests her chin on her hand. The collage background includes vintage newspaper clippings, floral motifs, a blue damask pattern, and details like an evil eye charm and 'I'M LITERALLY JUST A GIRL' sticker in pink.

A young woman takes a mirror selfie, covering her face with her phone. She wears a striped blue and white crop top, black high-waisted jeans with a double-ring belt, and a butterfly charm necklace. The background has large white hearts on a brown textured wall, creating a modern Pinterest aesthetic.

A hyper-realistic cinematic portrait of a couple standing together in the rain. The girl wears a drenched saree with raindrops on her skin and a soft romantic look, while the boy in a soaked white shirt gently holds her waist from behind. They smile and enjoy the rain, surrounded by glowing streetlights and a dreamy cinematic background.

A retro, vintage-inspired image—grainy yet bright—showing a girl in a blue cotton saree with small white flower prints and a white blouse, and a boy in a semi-formal retro outfit. They sit on a wooden bench surrounded by flying leaves, exuding a 90s romantic Pinterest vibe. The girl's hair has a small flower tucked in and both look at the camera under dramatic lighting.

A retro, vintage-inspired image—grainy yet bright—of a girl in an off-white cotton saree with a red blouse and a guy in an off-white kurta. She walks and looks back as the guy holds her saree pallu. They stand near an old wooden door with cinematic lighting, dramatic contrast, and romantic tension, evoking a nostalgic 90s movie scene.

A retro, vintage-inspired image—grainy yet bright—depicting a girl in a black cotton saree with white leaf prints and a white blouse, styled in a Pinterest aesthetic. The boy wears a blue short kurta with white chinos. She sits on a wooden bench reading a book while maple leaves fly in the air, creating a windy, cinematic 90s romantic atmosphere. The guy adjusts her hair while looking at her as she reads.

A retro, vintage-inspired image—grainy yet bright—featuring a girl in a perfect red retro saree and a boy in a white Chinese-collar kurta. The aesthetic captures a 90s romantic movie moment. Her wavy brown curls with a small flower tucked in blow in the wind as the boy holds her waist and looks deep into her eyes. They stand against a solid wall with dramatic light and shadows, creating an artistic cinematic mood.

A retro, vintage-inspired image—grainy yet bright—of a girl in an off-white cotton saree with a red blouse, styled in a Pinterest aesthetic. The guy wears an off-white kurta. They stand against an old wooden door with deep shadows and dramatic contrasts. The girl walks and looks back while the guy holds her saree pallu, gazing at her, evoking a moody, cinematic 90s movie scene.

A retro, vintage-inspired image—grainy yet bright—based on the reference picture. The girl is draped in a perfect brown Pinterest-style retro saree, and the boy is in a matching vintage brown suit. The mood feels like a 90s movie scene with a brown-haired baddie aesthetic, a small flower tucked into her curls, and a windy, romantic environment. They stand against a solid wall with deep shadows and dramatic contrast for a mysterious, artistic atmosphere.

A high-contrast, gritty street portrait of a man, late 20s, in front of a heavily textured, paint-peeling wall in an old neighborhood. Shot with a vintage film camera aesthetic, heavy grain and subtle color shift.
A glitch-art style headshot of a young man with a neutral pose, where digital static and neon geometric lines are subtly overlaid on the image, blending modern tech aesthetics with his face.
A low-key portrait (mostly dark tones) of an Indian musician (30s) with long hair, illuminated only by a single warm spotlight from above. Holding a guitar neck partially in the frame.
A hyper-realistic close-up of an Indian actor. Focus on the eyes, which are intense and direct. Shot with a wide-aperture lens against a completely out-of-focus, colorful background.
A cinematic headshot of an Indian man, mid-40s, with a serious expression. Dramatic chiaroscuro lighting, half his face in deep shadow and half intensely lit. Inspired by Caravaggio paintings.
A 'candid' moment of a man in a cafe, looking away from the camera, smiling slightly while holding a coffee cup. Warm, tungsten lighting, soft focus.
A photorealistic portrait of an Indian man with stylishly groomed hair and a simple grey hoodie, shot in soft, diffused evening light. Neutral expression, very high detail on hair strands.
A close-up headshot of a male fitness trainer, early 30s, short-cropped hair, wearing athletic wear. Sweat glistening slightly on his forehead. Against a dark, textured gym wall.
A travel blogger (20s) with a light beard, wearing a denim jacket. Smiling genuinely, facing a jungle or mountain backdrop (like the Himalayas). Bright, sunny daylight.

A casual, relaxed headshot of a man in a simple black t-shirt. Shot in an outdoor urban setting, like a busy street market in Delhi, but with the man sharply in focus and the background blurred (bokeh).
A portrait of a young artist from Kolkata wearing a simple cotton kurta, sitting with a cup of chai. Subtle, moody lighting filtering through a window pane. Extremely realistic skin texture.
A high-fashion, monochrome portrait of a modern man in a sophisticated black Bandhgala suit. Focus on the intricate texture of the fabric. Intense, direct gaze against a plain dark wall.

A candid portrait of an elderly Rajasthani gentleman with a distinguished mustache, wearing a vibrant, patterned turban. Deeply wrinkled face conveying wisdom. Shot with dramatic natural light, highly textured.
A close-up portrait of a South Indian groom (20s) wearing a traditional silk wedding dhoti and an ornate gold thread shawl (angavastram). Shot with soft, warm light in a temple courtyard.
A striking headshot of a Punjabi man in his late 20s wearing a crisp, ivory white kurta and a light saffron turban (pagdi). Shot outdoors during the Golden Hour, deep saturation.
A corporate headshot of a middle-aged, distinguished man, salt-and-pepper hair, in a classic pinstripe suit. Subtle catchlight in the eyes. Shot with a medium-format lens for extreme detail.
A Mumbai-based entrepreneur (30s) wearing a well-fitted light grey Nehru jacket over a white kurta. Clean, white studio background. Professional, approachable smile.
A mid-career Indian financial analyst (40s) in a charcoal grey suit. Shot in black and white, with dramatic, cinematic lighting. Slight furrow in the brow, conveying seriousness and expertise.

A young Indian software engineer in a light blue collared shirt and modern wire-frame glasses. Against a blurred, minimalist office background. Natural, window-side lighting, close-up, high-resolution photo.

A 35-year-old successful South Indian CEO in a tailored dark navy suit, seated at a mahogany desk. Gazing directly at the camera with a confident, open smile. Soft studio lighting. Depth of field effect.
